# BreakPong (Unity + C#)

A hybrid arcade game combining mechanics from Pong and Breakout. Built using Unity 2D.

---

## Gameplay Overview

Players control a paddle to keep the ball in play while breaking all bricks. The game includes scoring, game states, and restart mechanics.

---

## Features

- Paddle movement system
- Ball physics with collision reflection
- Brick destruction system
- Score tracking system
- Game over and restart system
- Basic UI (Main Menu / Gameplay / Game Over)

---

## Technical Highlights

- Unity Physics (Rigidbody2D, Colliders)
- Game state management (Menu → Playing → Game Over)
- Event-based scoring system
- Modular C# scripts (Paddle, Ball, GameManager)

